{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then I had to roll out the trolley from this bay, from the bay where-- where they-- the belt was, the conveyor belt was, and take it through a heavy iron door which opened outward.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I had to do it very fast so that no light should go out, especially at night, no light.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "In the dark, no light should go out because of air raids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And then put it on rails and let it down on the rails a very steep hill.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And at the end of the steep hill, stop it, jump aside, stop it, and-- and open up the offloading bays, iron door-- heavy iron door, which opened outward, again being careful that the light shouldn't come on.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Roll it in and then offload it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And at the stage where I offloaded them, I always offloaded them to trying-- to-- to-- in a way that I try to break the Bakelite cap and-- and-- so that I was pretty sure that any grenades that went out from my hands-- through my hands-- did not explode.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Now, we were never found out, but had we been found out, obviously we would have been shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] during the times that I let the trolley down this very steep hill on the rails, I always had someone to work the brakes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And for a while I had a German worker working the brakes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Now, this German worker had very gruff manner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "For some reason or other, I knew-- we were not allowed to speak, even though we were outside.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I mean, it was all outside, that it was-- but we were not allowed to speak.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And he had a very gruff manner.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
